266
00:13:49.129 --> 00:13:51.298
I always thought it was so
he could avoid the press.

267
00:13:51.332 --> 00:13:52.976
I guess it turns out it was
because he couldn't exactly

268
00:13:53.000 --> 00:13:55.336
