dressed as Batman.

269
00:13:57.071 --> 00:13:58.606
OK. but to even
access the elevator.

270
00:13:58.640 --> 00:14:00.107
we need to break
into the garage.

271
00:14:00.140 --> 00:14:01.384
and Wayne Security
patrols search

272
