I've just had to talk to.

303
00:15:11.211 --> 00:15:14.549
and they all have
exactly one question.

304
00:15:14.582 --> 00:15:16.950
When are we gonna catch 'em?

305
00:15:16.984 --> 00:15:18.796
But you know the number
that I'm most worried about?

306
00:15:18.820 --> 00:15:20.755
34... your approval rating?

307
00:15:20.789 --> 00:15:24.057
Zero. which is how
many leads you've got.

308
00:15:24.091 --> 00:15:27.094
Actually. there is one.

309
00:15:27.127 --> 00:15:28.929
Financial Crimes sent this over.

310
00:15:28.962 --> 00:15:30.264
The night of the convoy escape.

311
00:15:30.297 --> 00:15:33.033
every bank in Gotham was hacked.

312
00:15:33.066 --> 00:15:34.602
They were digging
through accounts

313
00:15:34.636 --> 00:15:36.003
