360
00:18:40.021 --> 00:18:41.421
I'm kinda digging
the name Harper.

361
00:18:43.057 --> 00:18:44.525
Whoa. Kidding. Hate that name.

362
00:18:44.559 --> 00:18:46.226
Look. I'm just saying that if...

363
00:18:46.259 --> 00:18:47.938
If proving we're innocent
means breaking into

364
00:18:47.962 --> 00:18:49.105
a place that we were very lucky

365
00:18:49.129 --> 00:18:50.206
to get out of the first time.

366
00:18:50.230 --> 00:18:51.331
we are better off running.

367
00:18:51.365 --> 00:18:53.001
Yeah. it takes money to run.

368
00:18:53.034 --> 00:18:54.377
I got that covered. I
did some asking around

369
00:18:54.401 --> 00:18:56.604
and this creepy.
little timepiece

370
00:18:56.638 --> 00:18:58.539
