ticket outta G-town.

381
00:19:22.864 --> 00:19:24.297
Come on.

382
00:19:24.331 --> 00:19:26.333
I'll even let you pick
the radio station.

383
00:19:49.057 --> 00:19:51.559
This is the last
place he was alive.

384
00:19:57.264 --> 00:19:59.167
Come on.

385
00:19:59.199 --> 00:20:00.500
We don't have much time.

386
00:20:33.266 --> 00:20:35.570
It's a good thing you
know your way around.

387
00:20:44.344 --> 00:20:46.379
That his most recent one?

388
00:20:46.413 --> 00:20:48.415
No. it's from when
he was just a kid.

389
00:20:49.584 --> 00:20:51.418
It's all about the
murder of his parents.

390
00:20:52.987 --> 00:20:54.321
