395
00:21:07.802 --> 00:21:09.771
but he didn't
orchestrate the murder."

396
00:21:11.438 --> 00:21:13.007
"The Court of Owls did."

397
00:21:18.478 --> 00:21:20.515
Heh. You seriously
can't be thinking of

398
