437
00:23:00.413 --> 00:23:03.284
OK. I know two things.

438
00:23:03.317 --> 00:23:05.753
One. Turner is innocent.

439
00:23:05.786 --> 00:23:08.356
And two. if you had
any proof against me

440
00:23:08.388 --> 00:23:09.666
