You don't want to
talk. OK. Fine.

446
00:23:34.582 --> 00:23:36.150
Looks like there's
someone who does.

447
00:23:38.019 --> 00:23:39.253
Yup.

448
00:23:39.287 --> 00:23:40.621
OK. You sure?

449
00:23:45.826 --> 00:23:48.495
Why would the Court
kill Bruce's parents?

450
00:23:48.529 --> 00:23:50.631
I don't know. And
according to this.

451
00:23:50.665 --> 00:23:52.533
