452
00:23:52.566 --> 00:23:53.944
He believed they murdered
his great-great-grandfather

453
00:23:53.968 --> 00:23:55.369
Alan Wayne.

454
00:23:55.403 --> 00:23:56.647
The guy who designed
this building?

455
00:23:56.671 --> 00:23:58.438
Yeah. My dad suspected

456
