they gathered in secret.

460
00:24:06.547 --> 00:24:07.815
What did he find?

461
00:24:09.850 --> 00:24:10.885
Nothing.

462
00:24:14.155 --> 00:24:16.524
"In the end. all
I was certain of

463
00:24:16.557 --> 00:24:18.559
"was that the Court
was a fairytale.

464
00:24:18.592 --> 00:24:20.194
"No more than a nursery rhyme

465
00:24:20.227 --> 00:24:21.796
