466
00:24:21.829 --> 00:24:24.598
"The only thing real was
my obsession with them.

467
00:24:24.632 --> 00:24:28.202
Despite my efforts. I found no
evidence they ever existed."

468
00:24:28.235 --> 00:24:30.380
I don't get it. He was investigating
the Court when he died.

469
00:24:30.404 --> 00:24:32.506
Something must have
changed his mind.

470
00:24:32.540 --> 00:24:34.875
Maybe it's in his last journal.

471
00:24:37.044 --> 00:24:38.512
Uh. what's that?

472
00:24:38.546 --> 00:24:40.247
Security alert.

473
00:24:40.281 --> 00:24:42.482
Uh. guys? All the
security cameras

474
00:24:42.516 --> 00:24:43.918
