just went offline.

475
00:24:43.951 --> 00:24:45.786
That's great. How'd
you manage that?

476
00:24:45.820 --> 00:24:47.755
I didn't. And I don't think

477
00:24:47.788 --> 00:24:49.423
security did. either. because

478
00:24:49.457 --> 00:24:50.725
they just notified the GCPD

479
00:24:50.758 --> 00:24:52.093
