going off on your floor.

482
00:24:56.397 --> 00:24:58.008
Security? No. There's no
patrols on your level.

483
00:24:58.032 --> 00:24:59.643
- Then who the hell is it?
- I don't know.

484
00:24:59.667 --> 00:25:02.737
but if you don't hurry.
you're gonna find out.

485
00:25:02.770 --> 00:25:04.414
- We're packing up now.
- Got his last journal.

486
00:25:04.438 --> 00:25:05.873
Come on. Let's go.

487
00:25:35.669 --> 00:25:40.207
Guys. talk to me.
Guys. what's happening?

488
00:25:40.241 --> 00:25:42.443
I think we just met the Talon.

489
00:25:46.515 --> 00:25:48.416
What the hell is that?

490
00:25:48.449 --> 00:25:49.926
Security alert just
went building wide.

491
00:25:49.950 --> 00:25:51.585
Wayne Security is

492
00:25:51.619 --> 00:25:53.120
