to you right now.

493
00:25:54.288 --> 00:25:55.524
Oh. Fun.

494
00:25:55.556 --> 00:25:56.724
GCPD is already inbound.

495
00:25:56.757 --> 00:25:58.392
You need to get out of there.

496
00:25:58.426 --> 00:25:59.860
A little stuck right now.

497
00:26:07.201 --> 00:26:08.335
We've gotta go help them.

498
00:26:18.979 --> 00:26:20.581
- Duela. no.
- They're about to be

499
00:26:20.614 --> 00:26:21.982
the meat in a
cop-Talon sandwich.

500
00:26:22.016 --> 00:26:23.951
This is your last
chance to stay alive.

501
00:26:23.984 --> 00:26:25.286
You can go with her if you want.

502
00:26:25.319 --> 00:26:26.487
Not without you.

503
00:26:26.521 --> 00:26:27.621
Duela. you can't do this.

504
00:26:27.655 --> 00:26:28.989
You can't just abandon them.

505
00:26:29.023 --> 00:26:31.392
Why not. Cullen?
Everyone abandoned me.

506
00:26:31.425 --> 00:26:32.702
Enough times for me to know that

507
00:26:32.726 --> 00:26:34.228
